snippet.textDisplay:
Brought me tears! Amazing!! 👏

First of all, excellent idea! All respect for the moment when the idea was generated! 💙
Kudos to project designers' efforts! ❤

Superb videograpghy; best thing was to time the NAMES' motion with Atif's arm/hand movements.👌👌

Atif's recitation was epic throughout yet intelligence poured enormously in last 7 or 8 NAMES. 💞

~Now completion would be recitation of 99 names of Prophet Muhammad (sallaaho alaihay wa alehi wasallam) before end of Ramazan. 💚 That effort would be something completing the package; picturing perfection.

Hats off xulfi & co. Hats off Atif! Hats off Coke Studio! 👏👌👍

P.S. I'm a very keen Music enthusiast and have been following CK since season 7; and never ever commented on any platform before this. Thus another kind of appreciation goes to this production for compelling me to this act. 😅♥
